lemma inter_guards_Seq: "(Seq a1 a2 \<inter>\<^sub>g c2) = Some c = (\<exists>b1 b2 d1 d2. c2=Seq b1 b2 \<and> (a1 \<inter>\<^sub>g b1) = Some d1 \<and> (a2 \<inter>\<^sub>g b2) = Some d2 \<and> c=Seq d1 d2)"
by (cases c2) (auto split: option.splits if_split_asm)
